  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Meatgrinder is a high-octane epic FPS. No cutscenes or storylines, just pure action. It's like if Clustertruck met Duke Nukem.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVING ENVIRONMENT</h2>Constantly moving environment won't let you rest for a second<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/f9da3b967647e73c73b734506d3869e9.poster.avif?t=1697706749\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/f9da3b967647e73c73b734506d3869e9.webm?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/f9da3b967647e73c73b734506d3869e9.mp4?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAST-PACED GAMEPLAY</h2>The game is really fast. You'll have to master your movement - jump, dodge and annihilate enemies before they even see you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/d457b69ecc4b2e25b61596f208afcf68.poster.avif?t=1697706749\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/d457b69ecc4b2e25b61596f208afcf68.webm?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/d457b69ecc4b2e25b61596f208afcf68.mp4?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHAOTIC AND INSANE</h2>Jump your way through insane levels on top of speeding trucks, trains and planes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/6ba113693412ddb5e498bb53677b9fc1.poster.avif?t=1697706749\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/6ba113693412ddb5e498bb53677b9fc1.webm?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1968710/extras/6ba113693412ddb5e498bb53677b9fc1.mp4?t=1697706749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
